scopecontent.p:
The 51 pamphlets in this section were published primarily by Pakistan
                     government offices and contain information on plans of the Karachi Development
                     Authority; planning and development of Pakistan cities; cooperative housing;
                     government incentives for public housing; the capital development authority;
                     and issues concerning city slums.
